I made the mistake of attaching the event in the loaded event of Window. For some reason the SKElement will refuse to draw and call the PaintSurface handler.

```
        public MainWindow()
        {
            InitializeComponent();
            this.Loaded += MainWindow_Loaded;
        }

        private void MainWindow_Loaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
        {
            this.skia.PaintSurface += this.Skia_PaintSurface;
        }

        private void Skia_PaintSurface(object sender, SKPaintSurfaceEventArgs args)
        {
            // paint stuff
        }
```
